Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 抱、抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但、但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那為什麼能進高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那、那是因為……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是跳級的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說腦袋非常的聰明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為應付課業綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以上課才會睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 好耀眼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.79,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,470)\1c&H3A9EF7&}#05 據說這就是經產婦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.79,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,470)\3c&HF2C855&\bord6}#05 據說這就是經產婦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}但是依然是一個普通的高中生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊 那明天的考試應該也很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天的考…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我正打算準備考試真白就穿著睡衣鬧起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 也好 考試什麼的小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是成績差會給姐姐大人丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼這裡會出現紅緒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是當然的吧 姐姐大人在學校很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她的妹妹要是成績差的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會給姐姐大人添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我覺得在這之前紅緒本人就有相當大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家都應該清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會添麻煩什麼的…那種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什、什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一旦無法用語言來表達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就會用行動來表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家裡寄信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說了「下次派人來看看狀況」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還想來看看真白是不是真的能吃黏糊糊食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你已經能吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 啊啊 這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未來有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個還不能說是能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒想到這麼快就會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那、那個 跟我也有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對啊 比起我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的事情更加重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是來看即將成為三峰家新娘的小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}料理  打掃  洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為一個…新…娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&HFFD997&}成績沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&H94F4FC&}家事萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&HD2B6F9&}巨乳安產型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼特別的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以矛頭會先指向我這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以是誰會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 可能是哪個親戚會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起裝的奇奇怪怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如讓他來看看平時的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以從今天開始真白碳的內衣就是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你連這個都買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種「平時」也可以讓別人看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了 還有其他什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考試結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 中午囉 去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 今天去學生食堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你沒去過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偶爾也吃點熱的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生食堂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an7\fs35\fad(100,0)}本週推薦！！ \N黏稠蓋飯 \N納豆+秋葵+山藥 \N魚子+海帶莖+生雞蛋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 家裡人要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊～ 畢竟立場是新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為來客人的話就要做些準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果要住的話就要準備房間還有準備餐點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}配合來客的年齡準備和食或者西餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}點心也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不用那麼操心也行啦...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然總是滿口抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅你其實已經默許了吧 白夜同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不…那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好玩不好玩一點也不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你問什麼東西不好玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是吐槽不能的這傢伙啊這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}光是救命恩人這一點就已經很狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是未婚夫什麼的是要怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本來是那麼黏姐姐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懲罰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是讓小紅受傷的我的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她只是正常的長大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然我很感謝白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我才是她最親近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果想談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒你能做到的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}與其說是戀愛 不如說是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的話那樣也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜你吃的是烏龍麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像都沒怎麼動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅做的更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被馴服了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馴服？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先想準備接待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是準備齊全比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}克服納豆的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從接觸開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從這裡開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說你穿成這樣會著涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會 難得收到的 不穿就浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 還是第一次穿這麼鮮豔的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心情有點複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喜歡啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 從三峰家過來的人會是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人和姐姐大人都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和她們相比 會怎麼看待我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在啊 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什 什…所以說要幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐也在呢 小紅碳
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…一町目的夜之森家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是 幾町目來著
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之 先做好不管客人什麼時候到都能迎接的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然可以做燒烤點心一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但接待客人的話還是從商店買比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜也來買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白託我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是為了習慣納豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蜂蜜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就換煉乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是迷路走到完全不相干的地方了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體不由自主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃 城裡的誘惑實在多到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在蘋果很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以做蘋果派了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 肉桂好像沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買一下 你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 你應該不知道是什麼樣的肉桂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是條狀 是粉狀不加糖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Goo、Google一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…我知道了你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是三町目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能找到二町目的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就到一町目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯 沒問題的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}鯛魚燒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}點心店
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}甜莓工廠
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一次次被誘惑打敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好險好險 還要買檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買一下你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才 很正常的交談了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一…一町目怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沿著這條路…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我剛好也去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶您過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}東西我幫您拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這孩子是？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx6\fry6\fs30\shad0\frz18.151\c&H4F4976&\3c&HAAA0D7&\pos(821,554)}烤麵包
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛來這一帶的人都不容易找到路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢 每條路上的房子都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和服～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是哪家的大小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}覺得您穿和服很合適 很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 那個 有點不適合穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 胸部的原因啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是叫做乾納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不也還是有納豆感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為納豆就是納豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問你要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不介意的話可以一起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是一町目的夜之森家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 你們兩個還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼是和小紅一起來的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我媽媽也可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開玩笑的～
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初次見面 我叫三峰白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和真白受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪裡哪裡 伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅途勞頓辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下是小紅的姐姐紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您累了吧 來請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是經產婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}啊啊啊 怎麼辦呢 居然來得這麼快 但是這樣也不能哭嗚 怎麼辦呢 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馬麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之先去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅凍結中？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡作為姐姐的我要振作起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能丟小紅的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇啊 我來做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是夜之森小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 嚇到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛開始有想過你會不會就是小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個我可以趁熱吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 媽媽今天在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然來之前先打了招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個時候在車站附近見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為來到這裡還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是轉來轉去 猶豫來猶豫去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迷路了那麼久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}經過一番猶豫 把巧克力味奶黃味還有原味的所有種類都買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}於是 你是來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫媽媽的真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是給真白的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你現在可以吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}信上是這樣寫著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 加油 加油 一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 還是吃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 撒些無聊的謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然自己想著有還是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明顯可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說回來 小紅真的長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明那時候那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 讓我摸一摸行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超級重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沉甸甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅這麼可愛的妹子是我家的兒媳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 可能是有點太急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}將來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們一族人也少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很難找到對象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 因為開發什麼的住的地方也越來越少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也嚐嚐這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且 白夜為了救小紅用了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦 這個也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係哦 我也會給真白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家也請嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一類的話題還沒告訴小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是人類的事情也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汪汪好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他叫做白夜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和牠做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黑呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可愛啊 好孩子好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也默默在想是不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白的高中生幼女體型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有看到媽媽的蘿莉婆婆體型…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不對 看到媽媽年輕的身材就一目了然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩位是妖精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是並不是大家都很小很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且白夜長得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人們對我們有許多稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}魔物 怪物 鬼 幽靈……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 還有「我老婆」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這稱呼倒還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是當然 突然聽到這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}怎麼了小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點躺下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能走到房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我抱你去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 白夜也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發燒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暈暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想起來…什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 退熱貼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 可能是事情發生得太突然 嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如 岳母是蘿莉什麼的很少見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這話不該我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被嚇到的不是那以外的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 媽媽我喋喋不休的說了多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明大家不像紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一顆鋼鐵的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}承蒙誇獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且這種事一般人不會說「啊 是這樣嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後相信的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看我就是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心靈美 坦誠的 童心未泯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}純潔的少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這種話是怎麼能冠冕堂皇的說出來的啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 果然是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受傷的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的很危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以白夜一著急 把自己一半的力量給了小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是因為是人類以外的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能有時身體還是會不適應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休息一下就能好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說…說了……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦啦 不好意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的事對大家要保密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否則我們就沒有立足之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 我明白了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是平時說了別人也不信呢 肯定會被說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「什麼 難道你腦內設定是這樣的嗎」 之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅也病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也差不多該告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個 也要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}注意身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黏呼呼的 要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腦內保存 腦內保存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 小紅醬也要多保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為啥來的時候坐的是一般交通工具咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為喜歡啊 坐車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那個外表用媽媽的口氣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該怎麼形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住一晚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳一定很想跟媽媽撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜他們不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是靠白夜的力量才得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這種話實在不能相信……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不信不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬以前摸過白夜的頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你跟他做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦 討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會惹白夜生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為自己很高興所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}認為摸別人 別人也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行李也挺重的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要快點回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鎮上的居民們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚有剛出爐的菠蘿麵包移動販賣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下 等一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等我～
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}菠蘿麵包10個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甜甜圈15個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}by 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臉真厚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 就用小姑來填補吧
